Reference:
    Daubert, T. E., & Danner, R. P. (1985).
    Data compilation tables of properties of pure compounds.

Notes:
    This file contains coefficients for NSRDS functions of temperature for
    interface properties of various liquids. More properties are provided by
    the reference. This is a subset containing only the properties that we
    typically require.

    The properties are provided for liquid compounds, but interface properties
    relate to a boundary between two phases. It is assumed that these
    properties relate to the specified liquid in contact with a gaseous phase,
    and that the property values are insensitive to the state of that gas. It
    is not clear over what range of conditions these assumptions remain valid.

\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
FoamFile
{
    format      ascii;
    class       dictionary;
    location    "constant";
    object      NSRDSinterfaceProperties;
}
